{"tid":1761703,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"提提大家關注2019年澳門新惡法：秘密警察法；謠言法；網絡安全法；送中法，唔想香港變澳門就同我入黎","createTime":"2019-11-29T05:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T06:08:11.000Z","uid":304769,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"668517fea116926a9a8a94af1b27508db2224845","tid":1761703,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:35:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n大家個個最近幾日<span style=\"color: red;\">淨係掛著係度慶祝，笑何已完，笑大陸人，笑雜種比人撚，HI到連抗爭都停埋</span>。<br />\n大家要千萬記住，唔抗爭，<span style=\"color: red;\">班狗就會開始捉人，手足就會開始比人清算，香港亦會極速變澳門</span>啦。<br />\n提翻大家，澳門有以下新惡法（或草案）：<br />\n網絡安全法（連手機都要實名）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/400954/%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%AF%A6%E6%96%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E9%A0%88%E5%AF%A6%E5%90%8D%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E5%8D%BB%E5%8F%AF%E4%BF%9D%E5%AF%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2595%25B8%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%2F400954%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B5%25A1%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%2596%25BD%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2588%25B6%25E9%25A0%2588%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%2590%258D%25E7%2599%25BB%25E8%25A8%2598-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599%25E5%258D%25BB%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AF%2586&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=92484a8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/400954/%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%AF%A6%E6%96%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E9%A0%88%E5%AF%A6%E5%90%8D%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E5%8D%BB%E5%8F%AF%E4%BF%9D%E5%AF%86</a><br />\n秘密警察法<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%B8%E8%AD%A6%E6%AC%8A%E5%8A%9B%E5%86%8D%E6%94%BE%E5%A4%A7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%25B8%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25A4%25A7%2F&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=bf7c660b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%25B8%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25A4%25A7%2F&h=bd6abcbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%B8%E8%AD%A6%E6%AC%8A%E5%8A%9B%E5%86%8D%E6%94%BE%E5%A4%A7/</a><br />\n謠言法<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80/%E5%8B%81%E9%81%8E-23-%E6%A2%9D-%E6%83%A1%E9%81%8E%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E6%B3%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E8%AC%A0%E8%A8%80%E7%BD%AA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%2F%25E5%258B%2581%25E9%2581%258E-23-%25E6%25A2%259D-%25E6%2583%25A1%25E9%2581%258E%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E8%25AC%25A0%25E8%25A8%2580%25E7%25BD%25AA%2F&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=f10e65b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%2F%25E5%258B%2581%25E9%2581%258E-23-%25E6%25A2%259D-%25E6%2583%25A1%25E9%2581%258E%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E8%25AC%25A0%25E8%25A8%2580%25E7%25BD%25AA%2F&h=a320a343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80/%E5%8B%81%E9%81%8E-23-%E6%A2%9D-%E6%83%A1%E9%81%8E%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E6%B3%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E8%AC%A0%E8%A8%80%E7%BD%AA/</a><br />\n送中法<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190505/59566022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190505%2F59566022&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=1c784be8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190505%2F59566022&h=aa0b4587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190505/59566022</a><br />\n<br />\n香港政治，軍事實力不足以同中國抗衡。<span style=\"color: green;\">要收中國皮，唯有經濟攬炒戰</span>，方法如下：<br />\n1.持續<span style=\"color: green;\">抗爭，令中國國企不能在港獲利</span>，如今中國經濟不景加上貿易戰泥足深陷，定必心急如焚<br />\n2.<span style=\"color: green;\">中國狗急跳牆</span>，做出<span style=\"color: green;\">各種錯誤決定，例如各種惡法，甚至出兵</span><br />\n3.<span style=\"color: green;\">外資（包括經過香港投資中國外資）被嚇走，中國陷入經濟危機</span><br />\n4. 中國<span style=\"color: green;\">大量企業倒閉，大量工人失業</span><br />\n&ldquo;國富民強，有飯吃不要講民主&rdquo;等不攻自破<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">大量失業人士勇武抗爭（大陸人勇武起來仲勁過我地）</span><br />\n最終達至<span style=\"color: green;\">政權不穩甚至被推翻</span>的目的<br />\n要達到以上目標，我們要：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: blue;\">持續不間斷抗爭</span><br />\n2.<span style=\"color: blue;\">走資</span>，確保<span style=\"color: blue;\">個人資產平安</span>，亦可留待<span style=\"color: blue;\">攬炒後重建香港用</span><br />\n3.廣開後路，<span style=\"color: blue;\">BNO平權</span>，加強<span style=\"color: blue;\">遊說全球對港採取更寬鬆移民政策</span>（台灣已經做緊，美國人權法亦容許有案底抗爭者移民）<br />\n做呢樣有幾個好處：<br />\na.<span style=\"color: blue;\">救手足</span><br />\nb.有太平門大家可以更加<span style=\"color: blue;\">無後顧之憂去抗爭和支持攬炒</span><br />\nc.攬炒後仍可以<span style=\"color: blue;\">賺外資重建香港</span><br />\nd.必要是時可以<span style=\"color: blue;\">在英國/台灣或者其他地方建立小香港，收留香港人，保育、傳承和推廣我們的語言、文化、精神</span><br />\ne.<span style=\"color: blue;\">提升香港人地位，拉開與支那垃圾的差距</span><br />\n4.拉攏<span style=\"color: blue;\">全球制裁中港官員（尤其五眼聯盟，申根公約，EU國家）</span><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家幫我推上熱門，幫手令手足醒下啦喂</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ee8419dfce797d8dbf0c0510e37efd809a563b61","tid":1761703,"uid":321255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031e741c0341248c8d8286468e7c34e847cb5fd5","tid":1761703,"uid":266755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T06:08:11.000Z","msg":"幚推，但澳門就真喺。。。。。。"}]}